She felt herself being pulled downward.  She could herself scream. 
but not feeling the air come out of her mouth or lungs.  She was 
pulled for what seamed an eternity.  She saw lights and colors fly 
past her as she was falling downward.  She felt something enfold her 
and surround her.  It felt heavy and cold.  She wondered if she was 
sent to the inferno.  She couldn't move.  She felt like she was 
sufficating, and couldn't breath.  She screamed but couldn't hear 
herself scream.  She tried to breath again.  Still she couldn't draw 
a breath.  She felt energy pulse through her. It surged and she felt 
a wave of heat cover her. She tried to breath again, only this time, 
she felt her lungs fill with air.  She could feel the air pass in 
through her mouth and into her lungs. She felt cold benieth her.  She 
envisioned a table. She was laying on a table.  She could hear 
noises. It was like being brought on line for the first time. The 
energy pulsed through her and if felt hot running through her body.  
She heard the noise of someone talking. But couldn't make out the 
words.  She tried to open her eyes, but the remained shut.  Then she 
heard a loud pounting sound, like thunder in her ears.  It was her 
spark, it was beating and pulsing with the energy that surged through 
her.  The thunder filled her ears and almost drowned her other senses.
She could barely hear anything else.  She felt another surge of 
energy and her body began to shake.  Her body shook and shivered.  
She then opened her eyes.  She was in a lab.  Tubes hooked into her 
body.  She saw the room around her moving and spinning.  She tried to 
call out, but couldn't.  As her lungs again filled with air, she 
tried to speak again. She couldn't yet. She closed her eyes and let 
her body shake as the energy filled and pulsed into and through her.
